title: Alawar Games - Paradise Quest - New Match 3 - Wendy99
description:
Paradise Quest - 120.55 MB


Deep within the Galapagos archipelago, drastic climate changes have adversely affected the 
majestic island of Isabela. Help Dr. Evan Finch bring life back to this once magnificent retreat. 
Embark on a wild match-three adventure as you revive lush vegetation, restore a mighty animal 
kingdom and recover the secrets of a lost island in Paradise Quest. Restore each region of the 
island and attract wildlife to successfully revive the gorgeous surroundings of Isabela!


    * 15 powerups to unlock
    * 32 environmental upgrades
    * 350 habitat fragments to collect
    * 75 Galapagos species to document
    * Six island regions to restore
